title: 2010.05.23-MotoGP.04.France.Race.BBC2_UK [TDMK1]
description:
2010.05.23-MotoGP.04.France.Race.BBC2_UK-TDMK1.m4v

Jennie Gow introduces coverage of the third round of the season at Le Mans, where Jorge Lorenzo was successful last year. The Spaniard already has a win and a second place to show for his efforts this year, and leads the standings by four points from Italy's Valentino Rossi heading into the race. With commentary by Steve Parrish and Charlie Cox.

Now encoded as 'MP4 All Play'... As a departure from the DivX files which I have uploaded in the past, I've made the decision to get with the 21st century & start encoding with the following specs this year;

MP4 - 640x352 - 800Kb/s H264 Video - 44.1KHz/128Kbps Stereo AAC Audio

My belief is this is the best all round setup, and hopefully you will agree!

This video will play on a computer with VLC, XBMC, XBox360, PS3, iPad and all iPhones - enjoy the show... :)
